related_questions.question: What is a swamp cabbage?
related_questions.snippet: A unique food source consumed during scarce times by early pioneers. Sometimes referred to as the "Heart of Palm," swamp cabbage is the center core of the Sabal Palm Tree. Harvesting this edible portion of the plant results in the death of the tree.
